title: Expansion draft for Golden State Valkyries set for Dec. 6
description: The expansion draft, the league's first since 2008, for the Golden State Valkyries, who will launch play in 2025, will be held on Dec. 6 and air on ESPN, the WNBA announced on Monday.

title: WNBA playoff schedule 2024: Scores, news and highlights
description: New York is up 1-0 over two-time defending champ Las Vegas, and Connecticut won on the road to lead Minnesota 1-0 in the WNBA semifinals.

title: Marina Mabrey leads Connecticut Sun to Game 1 victory
description: Connecticut standout guard Marina Mabrey scored 20 points and connected on six 3-pointers in the Sun's 73-70 road victory over the favored Minnesota Lynx in Game 1 of their matchup in the WNBA semifinals at the Target Center on Sunday night.

title: Breanna Stewart, aiming for playoff atonement, rolls through Aces
description: Breanna Stewart had 34 points in New York's Game 1 win over the Aces, continuing her goal of making up for what she said was a subpar performance in last year's playoffs.
